Liz Hurley turned 57 on June 10 as the actress and model marked her birthday with a series of breathtaking photos. The British star looked stunning as she rocked a bold, off-the-shoulder, yellow dress which gave a glimpse of her cleavage as she leaned into the camera. The chic number featured sheer detail as she posed confidently in the fields. In view of her 2.3 million followers, she captioned the post: "Happy Birthday to meeeeeee 2022 @versace @donatella_versace." The beauty was inundated with birthday messages from her legion of followers.